_sText:
This is just simple map, it took me few minutes to make, not
even a hour.

So here's what is inside the map:

- Two wooden planks on sides (breakable)
- Large pit in the middle
- Grenade above the pit on a wooden plank (breakable)
- 2 exactly same spawns
- Few crates
- Side room on each side
- Some more crates
